Summary: Something unidentified in photo of friends
divs: Sighting DetailsA friend of mine had a pic taken of himself and friends at a pool here. We can't figure out what this object is that appears in only one shot and not the second shot taken only a few seconds later. No one saw the object until we looked at the pic later on the next day. This is really confusing. We would like to be contacted about this.
